All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
App
Application class with main method which provides manual interaction with elevator system.
Elevator
Model class for one elevator.
ElevatorDirection
Enum specifying direction of elevator.
ElevatorEngine
Class responsible for moving and changing direction of elevators.
ElevatorSelector
Class responsible for picking best suited elevators to floor where elevator was ordered.
ElevatorStatus
Class used to store status data about each elevator.
ElevatorSystem
Class responsible for controlling elevators in system.
InstructionsHandler
Class responsible for handling user instruction.
InstructionsParser
Class responsible for parsing user provided commands to instructions.
InstructionsReader
Class responsible for reading user input in command line.
OptionsParser
Class responsible for parsing initial program arguments: floors amount, elevators amount.
OrderDirection
Enum specifying direction of Order.
Passenger
Model class which contains data about passenger like pickup floor, target floor and elevator assigned to him.
